title: scriba
abstract: >-
  Free, local, accurate speaker-diarized meeting transcription for AI assistants
  and second brains. 100% on-device (whisperX + pyannote), agent-agnostic via
  AGENTS.md, with optional GigaAM-RU for Russian.
